{"tid":1992853,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【和你sing 2.0】喺避免重複而玩爛策略嘅同時，小心單一次嘅失敗被spin做「註定失敗」嘅理據","createTime":"2020-04-28T11:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T02:53:02.000Z","uid":131691,"like":63,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"150c740505b4325d7dd08f09bb80bb0f99eea772","tid":1992853,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:23:48.000Z","msg":"上星期，太古 和你sing Remaster之後已經有人提醒：唔好玩爛一招，要記得變通+進化，所以我唔再多講呢點。<br />\n<br />\n但係有第二點其實同樣重要：抗爭reboot之後，唔好又再次因爲單一次嘅失敗而自我封關，bam咗成個系列嘅策略。6月起實在有太多次「因爲一次失敗就吹奏到註定失敗」嘅自我催眠。<br />\n<br />\n記住：有挫折係正常，因爲警甴就算弱智都識得進化，但係挫折唔係直接放棄嘅藉口，反而係推動進化嘅誘因。"},{"pid":"7655e3fcfaddae70c71905f7b9dab9ee4142cca5","tid":1992853,"uid":33984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2de318d3177baa629436e3d97608c894c344acd","tid":1992853,"uid":131691,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:25:18.000Z","msg":"（今日無出，你們可以批鬥我了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"4ba0b59c12defadc03a64c7e6cf4d29500dd3d66","tid":1992853,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:26:50.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"89157d9846eb3d8933651846f47051ab55917385","tid":1992853,"uid":201492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:43:27.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"9b924ea58187037e9b65a483bcaffa7b0f5dd2c0","tid":1992853,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:50:18.000Z","msg":"【Be Water】流水式聚集 對抗限聚令<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992891</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1b341831eefcd48fcd307bd805be5136